Package com.bfo.zeroconf

Class Service

java.lang.Object
com.bfo.zeroconf.Service
public class Service extends Object
Service represents a new Service to be announced by the Zeroconf class, or an existing service which has been announced on the network. To create a new Service, see the Service.Builder subclass.
